{"tid":1656580,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"檢查你電話有冇呢類中資 Beauty Cam App","createTime":"2019-10-15T16:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T16:03:41.000Z","uid":1130,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b437de66eefc20c4eda3c2e4be97dfd7d0acdb2c","tid":1656580,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=713093519172997&amp;id=100014170657783\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D713093519172997%26id%3D100014170657783&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLLhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=acd388f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=713093519172997&amp;id=100014170657783</a><br />\n<br />\n以下文章針對hk app store<br />\n談談cosplayer常用的照騙app：<br />\nEg.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美圖秀秀、ulike、<br />\nO2cam、無他、<br />\nFoodie(日、韓版安全）</span><br />\n都是由中國科技公司開發，<br />\n有些則是地區特製版本，日本/韓國store的沒有相關條款<br />\n<br />\n而中國app都有自動送中條款，自動send你張相去北京server：<br />\n-用你的樣子做ai辨識<br />\n-用你的相片不知幹嘛，反正你同意<br />\n-咪高鋒權限偷聽你日常談話內容（已證實即使關了權限）仍然沒用<br />\n-gps存取你活動行程記錄<br />\n-有些app還會莫名其妙的要電話你聯絡人權限<br />\n如果你電話好多敏感資料、相、片，我恭喜你！<br />\n<br />\n總結：刪app保平安，還有記得安裝app之前看看條款和權限、開發者來自哪裡<br />\n請注意網絡安全，勿做豬隊友<br />\n*台灣朋友查一查app的公司開發者是不是來自中國的便可以了<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其他的中資危險相機app名單：<br />\n輕顏相機、黃油相機、泡芙相機、相機360、FaceU、Nomo、天天p圖</span><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">安全</span>的app名單：<br />\nSnow、B612、Looks 、原版Soda(日韓區）、原版Foodie(日韓區）、Moru、Pictail、facetune、Enlight 、PicArts 、VSCO<br />\n其他app歡迎補充"},{"pid":"80c00bac4906d3366f69886ee42ae91321d7f340","tid":1656580,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zBif5mg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzBif5mg.jpg&h=44757529&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9c3c41cc1a2563411d33c1401f7e90ea4e2908dc","tid":1656580,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/16/000333_d2c331b901ab6d1a2e77bf9b578c767e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F16%2F000333_d2c331b901ab6d1a2e77bf9b578c767e.jpg&h=7a53bd42&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}